# Authentication Tests for Ethiopian Job Search Backend
# Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/auth

### 1. Register a New User (Job Seeker)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoee",
  "email": "john.doee@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "confirmPassword": "securepass123",
  "user_type": "job_seeker"
}

### 2. Verify Email (Replace token from Register response)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "PASTE_REGISTER_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 3. Login with Email
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### 4. Login with Username
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "johndoe",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

